# Root .gitignore for Nativo-App Repository

### OS Files ###
.DS_Store
.DS_Store?
._*
.Spotlight-V100
.Trashes
ehthumbs.db
Thumbs.db
Desktop.ini
$RECYCLE.BIN/

### IDE - VS Code ###
# Uncomment if you want to ignore personal VS Code settings
# .vscode/
# Keep .vscode/ committed if it contains team-shared settings

### IDE - JetBrains (IntelliJ, WebStorm, etc.) ###
.idea/
*.iws
*.iml
*.ipr

### Logs ###
*.log
logs/
log/

### Temporary Files ###
*.tmp
*.temp
*.cache
*.bak
*.backup
*.old
*~
*.swp
*.swo

### Node.js (if frontend is added later) ###
node_modules/
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
.pnpm-debug.log*

### Python (if scripts are added) ###
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class
*.so
.Python

### Docker ###
docker-compose.override.yml
.dockerignore

### Build Artifacts (general) ###
dist/
build/
out/

### Coverage Reports ###
coverage/
*.cover
.coverage
htmlcov/

### Database Files ###
*.db
*.sqlite
*.sqlite3

### Uploads & Runtime Data ###
uploads/
temp/
cache/

### Documentation Generated ###
docs/generated/
docs/api/generated/

### Kiro ###
# Ignore all Kiro files


